{"tid":2361141,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"船長及3名船員染疫","createTime":"2021-01-10T11:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T18:50:59.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bee09e15dc9a3bd9acafa6ffc29b049eeb7ad5ba","tid":2361141,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:33:55.000Z","msg":"本港新冠肺炎疫情持續，衞生署公布今日（10日）新增31宗確診個案，3宗為輸入個案、28宗為本地個案，其中9宗個案為源頭不明，患者年齡介乎7歲至80歲。另外，今日有30多宗初步確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君醫生指，港九小輪有1名船長（編號9240）確診，屬無源頭個案，經追蹤後發現3名船員亦初步確診，目前正追蹤他們的緊密接觸者和行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君指，該船長會駕駛多條路線，包括荃灣至機場三跑、中環至坪洲，以及中環至榕樹灣等，他們在洗船、維修、休息、用膳等時間有較密切接觸，由於他們並非固定行駛同一航線、同一更份工作，故會追蹤曾經同更工作的同事，並已要求逾百名船員接受檢測。"},{"pid":"ed6f05ed35e90a17b4242ada80abbba3083084c7","tid":2361141,"uid":73241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:35:08.000Z","msg":"布船長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a14e559b73895f1ea9be5ec22428bf4683572e","tid":2361141,"uid":198008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78043ae9525e02afdd1ea7e069c13434a578e346","tid":2361141,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11a14e559b73895f1ea9be5ec22428bf4683572e","tid":2361141,"uid":198008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f9c0258331009daf0a4161f83f0eec372eeef7","tid":2361141,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11a14e559b73895f1ea9be5ec22428bf4683572e","tid":2361141,"uid":198008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:40:46.000Z","msg":"gateway<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a82ef2108bf6924bce921c1143f879b9c3696b","tid":2361141,"uid":159890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T18:31:50.000Z","msg":"無限手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e43ce1f17bd651888e31b2cb9a545c18e11b6da","tid":2361141,"uid":271130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T18:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲以為係你呀船長"}]}